    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Long linen altar cloths, as wide as the altar top and hanging over the sides, upon which the eucharist is celebrated.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
